name: PETRUK DADI RATU
description:
Petruk is one of the characters in the puppet world who is described as tall and long-nosed, clean-faced, patient, and loyal. He also has a submissive character, less intelligent and less skilled. With him it will be a problem if Petruk appears as a leader. He does not understand anything that can be reached, there are obligations, beliefs, responsibilities, character, and capacity of a king so that the kingdom he leads becomes chaotic.Therefore, he only uses his short power to get pleasure in the world, without the vision and mission of a leader
